{
  "stem": "7455.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One time, I went into the stall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I said was attaching the chain, a fly must've bit the cow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she like moved and stepped on my toe with all her weight, with the hoof on my foot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I-- the more I tried to free myself, the deeper she embedded her foot into-- her hoof into my foot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Immediately, when I pushed her, my foot was covered with blood, mixed with a manure there, which caused an infection.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I limped into the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when [? we see it-- ?] then when I washed it away, and put some bandages on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But it was hurting me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the next day, I cannot go-- I could not go to the pasture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In fact, she went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She was sitting because the cow-- even though they give out grain and other thing-- needs the grass.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of the boys, knowing the cow, they know it's Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Winer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They walked over, and they said, how's your niece?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why is she not here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she, not realizing, says, she's not my niece.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She works for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The boys realized that I told a lie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As primitive as they were, they were clever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I stayed away for some time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very upset because if I can-- she cannot use my services, she's going to send me away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then she kept the cow in the stall and-- and did not take her up any more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After two weeks, it healed because it was infected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She did not call a doctor-- it was very badly infected-- because perhaps she suspected I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She didn't want any exposure for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I came back on the hill already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the boy, Miron-- he was my tormentor-- he came over.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
